<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD赢V3、PSG赢LGD、V3赢PSG。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但是LGD输给R7、PSG；V3赢R7。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">所以V3第二，PSG第三，LGD第四。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD和PSG打BO5，胜者再和A组第二打BO5，赢了才能晋级。</strong></p>
<p><strong>1.2.</strong></p>
<p><strong>V3赢PSG，UOL输R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD 2/2、V3 2/2、PSG 2/2、 UOL 2/2、R7 2/2</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">五队平分。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>则用时最长的两支队伍加赛淘汰一支。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>1.3.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3输PSG，UOL赢R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD 2/2、V3 1/3、PSG 3/1、UOL 3/1、R7 1/3</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD第三，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">V3和R7加赛争夺第四。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD和胜者打BO5，胜者再和A组第二打BO5，赢了才能晋级。</strong></p>
<p><strong>1.4.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3输PSG，UOL输R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD 2/2、V3 1/3、PSG 3/1、UOL 2/2、R7 2/2</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD、UOL、R7平分。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">R7赢LGD、LGD赢UOL，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">所以R7第二、LDG第三，UOL第四</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD和UOL打BO5，胜者再和A组第二打BO5，赢了才能晋级。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>情况二.LGD赢V3、输UOL</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2.1</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3赢PSG，UOL赢R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD1/3，UOL 4/0，PSG 2/2，V3 2/2，R7 1/3</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD和R7加赛，败者淘汰。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2.2</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3赢PSG，UOL输R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD1/3，UOL 3/1，PSG 2/2，V3 2/2，R7 2/2</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD第五，淘汰。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2.3</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3输PSG，UOL赢R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD1/3，UOL 4/0，PSG 3/1，V3 1/3，R7 1/3</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD、V3、R7同分，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD赢V3、V3赢R7、R7赢LGD，三队互有胜负，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>则用时长的两支加赛，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>胜者再和另一只队伍打BO5，胜者再和A组第二打BO5，赢了才能晋级。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2.4</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3输PSG，UOL输R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD1/3，UOL 3/1，PSG3/1，V3 1/3，R7 2/2</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD、V3同分，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD和V3加赛，败者淘汰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>情况三.LGD输V3、赢UOL</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>3.1</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3赢PSG，UOL赢R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD1/3，UOL 3/1，PSG 2/2，V3 3/1，R7 1/3</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD和R7同分，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD和R7加赛，败者淘汰</strong></p>
