<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>V3赢PSG，UOL输R7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">LGD1/3，UOL 2/2，PSG 2/2，V3 3/1，R7 2/2</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LGD淘汰。</strong></p>
